cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the integration of WSNs and cloud services to work autonomously in an IoT environment. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper describes a scalable system architecture that integrates WSNs and cloud services. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper mentions the use of a reinforcement learning algorithm to make decisions based on the environment's evolution. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of data analytics tools to execute a reinforcement learning algorithm. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper mentions the use of a mechanism to reduce the number of transmissions without compromising the data quality.
